trade protectionism is gaining ground , and realizing freedom , fairness , and justice is still a long - term and arduous task .
the struggle against terrorism is arduous and complicated , and non - traditional security factors have increased .
our world is still far from tranquil .
although the international community is still faced with various problems and may not be so idealistic in the future , the tide of peace and development is irreversible , and the desire of the people of all countries to live a better life has not changed .
it is of great significance that this dialogue meeting is focusing on development .
development is the foundation for the progress of human civilization and is the key to resolving all kinds of contradictions and problems facing the world .
only by achieving global coordination , balance , and universal development can lasting peace and stability be realized in the world .
we should explore this issue comprehensively and thoroughly , and work with concerted efforts to resolve this issue .
