under the impetus of the trend of economic globalization , the contacts between various countries and regions have become closer with each passing day , the market has become more open , and the flow of capital , technology , and talent has become more extensive and rapid . all these have brought about unprecedented opportunities for strengthening international cooperation and promoting common development .
